        <comment xml:lang="en">Mass of organic carbon in waste (without inorganic carbon), initially put in residual material landfill. The exchange represents a flow that is within the technosphere. This exchange should only be used to apply ecofactors for the Swiss LCIA method of Ecological Scarcity and not any other purpose.</comment>
